  "body": "# Feature\r\n\r\nImplement the \"Bottom Actions\" component in the quo2 component library.\r\n\r\n⚠️ NOTE: The component has the property `scroll` in Figma. Please exclude that prop for this issue, as we have an issue with Blur. We will implement it once we resolved the Blur issue.\r\n\r\n<img width=\"500\"  src=\"https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/assets/19339952/2b013385-000e-4e66-b9f5-116f809caa75\">\r\n\r\n### Designs\r\n\r\n[Link to Figma](https://www.figma.com/file/WQZcp6S0EnzxdTL4taoKDv/Design-System-for-Mobile?type=design&node-id=2500%3A41324&mode=design&t=Fx9sPvHE1N10Zx4e-1)\r\n\r\n### Acceptance Criteria:\r\n\r\n- Should follow the [best practices](https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/blob/develop/doc/new-guidelines.md)\r\n- Should add [component test](https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/blob/develop/doc/component-tests-overview.md)\r\n- Should add an export from the `quo2.core` namespace\r\n- Add a preview for this component under the `drawer` category in the Quo2 preview screen\r\n",
